 Current Head of House Erica has expressed regret for choosing Prince as her deputy. Erica made this statement after her fall out with Laycon on Saturday night. She told Trickytee and Kiddwaya she regrets choosing Prince as Deputy HOH. The trained actress said Prince is the biggest mistake she ever made because he didn’t take her side during her outburst with Laycon.  “You are the biggest mistake I ever made,” Erica said while Prince walked past her, Trickytee and Kiddwaya in the garden. “I made mistake picking Prince, I felt guilty picking him then, he has the guts not to pick my side. “I don’t mind going home tomorrow. Prince is an asshole, I regret choosing him as deputy head of house.”